                     <interp inst="t17840915-14-off63" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17840915-14-cd64" type="crimeDate">20th day of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17840915-14-off63 t17840915-14-cd64"></join>, one silver pinto mug, value 3 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17840915-14-victim260" type="victimName">
                           William 
                           Barnard
