                     <interp inst="t17840915-14-verdict66" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder40s"></interp>
               GUILTY, 30 s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840915-14-punish67" type="punishmentDescription">
